      <description>&lt;p&gt;#&amp;ldquo;Connecting to your Raspberry Pi desktop over the network&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;sudo apt-get install xrdp&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
Then run Remote Desktop on your Windows 7 PC to view the RPi desktop. Works just as well with VNC.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Simples. And works surprisingly well.&lt;/p&gt;

